GO analysis of each mature neturophil cluster

neuts.mat.sub = subset(neuts, idents = c("TREM1+MME+mat_neut","TNFAIP3+CXCL8+mat_neut","RETN+LCN2+mat_neut"))
DimPlot(neuts.mat.sub)

mature.neut.norm = as.matrix(neuts.mat.sub$tissue == "BM")

# 23913 11935 
mature.neut.norm.T = mature.neut.norm[mature.neut.norm %in% TRUE,]

## [1] 11935
mature.neut.norm.barcodes = names(mature.neut.norm.T)

trem1.markers  = FindMarkers(neuts.mat.sub, ident.1 = "TREM1+MME+mat_neut", min.pct = 0.2)
cxcl8.markers  = FindMarkers(neuts.mat.sub, ident.1 = "TNFAIP3+CXCL8+mat_neut", min.pct = 0.2)
retn.markers = FindMarkers(neuts.mat.sub, ident.1 = "RETN+LCN2+mat_neut", min.pct = 0.2)

Biological process Gene Ontology analysis for TREM1+MME+ mature neutrophils

degs_trem1= rownames_to_column(trem1.markers, var = "gene")
degs_trem1= degs_trem1%>% filter(avg_log2FC >0.85)
gene_symbols_trem1 = unique(degs_trem1$gene)

entrez_ids_trem1 = mapIds(org.Hs.eg.db, keys = gene_symbols_trem1, column = "ENTREZID", keytype = "SYMBOL", multiVals = "first")
## 'select()' returned 1:1 mapping between keys and columns
degs_trem1$entrez_id = entrez_ids_trem1[match(degs_trem1$gene, names(entrez_ids_trem1))]
go_trem1 = enrichGO(gene = degs_trem1$entrez_id,
                     OrgDb = org.Hs.eg.db,
                     ont = "BP",
                     pAdjustMethod = "BH",
                     qvalueCutoff = 0.1,
                     readable = TRUE)

go_terms_trem1 = as.data.frame(go_trem1)
go_terms_trem1$pvalue = as.numeric(go_terms_trem1$pvalue)

ggplot(go_terms_trem1, aes(x = reorder(Description, -log10(qvalue)), y = -log10(qvalue))) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(x = "GO Terms", y = "-log10(q-value)", title = "Top Enriched GO Terms")

ggplot(go_terms_trem1, aes(x = GeneRatio, y = reorder(Description, -log10(qvalue)), size = Count, color = -log10(qvalue))) +
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_color_gradient(low = "blue", high = "red") +
  labs(x = "Gene Ratio", y = "GO Terms", title = "GO Term Enrichment in TREM1+MME+mat_neut")

Biological process Gene Ontology analysis for TNFAIP3+CXCL8+ mature neutrophils

degs_cxcl8= rownames_to_column(cxcl8.markers, var = "gene")
degs_cxcl8= degs_cxcl8%>% filter(avg_log2FC >0.85)
gene_symbols_cxcl8 = unique(degs_cxcl8$gene)

entrez_ids_cxcl8 = mapIds(org.Hs.eg.db, keys = gene_symbols_cxcl8, column = "ENTREZID", keytype = "SYMBOL", multiVals = "first")
## 'select()' returned 1:1 mapping between keys and columns
degs_cxcl8$entrez_id = entrez_ids_cxcl8[match(degs_cxcl8$gene, names(entrez_ids_cxcl8))]
go_cxcl8 = enrichGO(gene = degs_cxcl8$entrez_id,
                    OrgDb = org.Hs.eg.db,
                    ont = "BP",
                    pAdjustMethod = "BH",
                    qvalueCutoff = 0.1,
                    readable = TRUE)

go_terms_cxcl8 = as.data.frame(go_cxcl8)
go_terms_cxcl8$pvalue = as.numeric(go_terms_cxcl8$pvalue)

ggplot(go_terms_cxcl8[1:30,], aes(x = reorder(Description, -log10(qvalue)), y = -log10(qvalue))) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(x = "GO Terms", y = "-log10(q-value)", title = "Top Enriched GO Terms")

go_terms_cxcl8.mini = go_terms_cxcl8$Description %in% go_terms_cxcl8$qvalue < 0.01
go_terms_cxcl8.minilist = go_terms_cxcl8[go_terms_cxcl8.mini,]

ggplot(go_terms_cxcl8.minilist[1:15,], aes(x = GeneRatio, y = reorder(Description, -log10(qvalue)), size = Count, color = -log10(qvalue))) +
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_color_gradient(low = "blue", high = "red") +
  labs(x = "Gene Ratio", y = "GO Terms", title = "GO Term Enrichment in TNFAIP3+CXCL8+mat_neut")

Biological process Gene Ontology analysis for RETN+LCN2+ mature neutrophils

degs_retn= rownames_to_column(retn.markers, var = "gene")
degs_retn= degs_retn%>% filter(avg_log2FC >0.85)
gene_symbols_retn = unique(degs_retn$gene)

entrez_ids_retn = mapIds(org.Hs.eg.db, keys = gene_symbols_retn, column = "ENTREZID", keytype = "SYMBOL", multiVals = "first")
## 'select()' returned 1:1 mapping between keys and columns
degs_retn$entrez_id = entrez_ids_retn[match(degs_retn$gene, names(entrez_ids_retn))]
go_retn = enrichGO(gene = degs_retn$entrez_id,
                     OrgDb = org.Hs.eg.db,
                     ont = "BP",
                     pAdjustMethod = "BH",
                     qvalueCutoff = 0.1,
                     readable = TRUE)

go_terms_retn = as.data.frame(go_retn)
go_terms_retn$pvalue = as.numeric(go_terms_retn$pvalue)

ggplot(go_terms_retn[1:30,], aes(x = reorder(Description, -log10(qvalue)), y = -log10(qvalue))) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(x = "GO Terms", y = "-log10(q-value)", title = "Top Enriched GO Terms")

go_terms_retn.mini = go_terms_retn$Description %in% go_terms_retn$qvalue < 0.01
go_terms_retn.minilist = go_terms_retn[go_terms_retn.mini,]

go_terms_retn.minilist = go_terms_retn.minilist[go_terms_retn.minilist$qvalue < 0.001,]

ggplot(go_terms_retn.minilist[1:14,], aes(x = GeneRatio, y = reorder(Description, -log10(qvalue)), size = Count, color = -log10(qvalue))) +
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_color_gradient(low = "blue", high = "red") +
  labs(x = "Gene Ratio", y = "GO Terms", title = "GO Term Enrichment in RETN+LCN2+mat_neut")

Heatmap of differentially expressed transcripts in mature neutrophils

x = FindAllMarkers(neuts.mat.sub, min.pct = 0.2, verbose = TRUE)
## Calculating cluster TREM1+MME+mat_neut
## Calculating cluster TNFAIP3+CXCL8+mat_neut
## Calculating cluster RETN+LCN2+mat_neut
mat.neut.sub.top25 <- x %>%
  group_by(cluster) %>%
  top_n(n = 25, wt = avg_log2FC)

neuts.mat.sub.small = subset(neuts.mat.sub, downsample = 3000)
DoHeatmap(neuts.mat.sub.small, features = mat.neut.sub.top25$gene, draw.lines = F, size = 3)+ 
  theme(text = element_text(size = 3))+
  scale_fill_gradientn(colors = c("royalblue", "snow2", "orangered"))+ theme(text = element_text(size = 4))
